name: Rancho Coronado
description: Rancho Coronado is one of the sub-districts of Santo Domingo, located in southeastern Night City. Rancho Coronado appears as a self-sufficient town within Night City. The corporations who own the Arroyo factories planned and advertised it as a place for their workers to live out the real American dream. Rancho Coronado consists almost solely of identical houses, reminiscent of the ones seen in mid twentieth century American suburbs. The district has its own bars, shops, school, park...
